<form method='POST' action='/dashboard/profile/create' enctype='multipart/form-data'>
  <h3>Tailor your profile!</h3>
  <h4>So the internet is the digital wild wild west, carefully curate your profile so you can stand out from the rest of your peers; afterall you don't want to be known as that weird guy right??</h4>
  <h4>Girls, show your insta-gram worthy photos, Guys show your 'do you lift bro' poses!</h4>
  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="exampleInputDescrib">Description</label>
    <input type="text" class="form-control" name="description" placeholder="write a quotable quote about yourself, something like YOLO, didnt read or 'POP-POP!'">
  </div>
  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="file-upload" id=uploadComplete>Upload a profile picture!<input id="file-upload" type="file" name="avatar"></label>
  </div>
  <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default btn-primary">Submit</button>
</form>
